      "content": "Skip to content Partner with Central Florida Animal Reserve Home » Get Involved » Partner CFAR Partnership Programs Partnerships with Central Florida Animal Reserve provide businesses and organizations with meaningful, year-round ways to support animal care, education, and operations while building long-term alignment with CFAR’s mission.CFAR offers two primary partnership pathways: Annual Partners Program Scholarship Sponsor Program Understanding CFAR Support Opportunities CFAR offers several ways for businesses to support the mission, each with a different focus. Partners Partners provide annual, mission-wide support that sustains CFAR’s operations throughout the year. Partnerships focus on long-term engagement, recurring visibility, and deeper integration with CFAR’s work. Sponsors Sponsors typically support specific initiatives or on-site needs, such as Feed the Kitty or In-Kind contributions. Event Sponsors Event Sponsors support individual events, such as fundraisers or special programs, with recognition tied to that specific event. Annual Partners Program Partners Program provides businesses with year-round visibility and engagement opportunities with CFAR’s audience. These sponsors support our overall mission and operations on an annual basis. These are extended on a rotating 12-month basis, renewed on the Partner’s anniversary. Super Hero Partner $10,000 per year Benefits All Hero Partner benefits Exclusive sponsorship of a specific habitat or enclosure, with plaque Logo on CFAR e-promotions for all ticketed and group events Featured article in quarterly newsletters Private VIP tour and luncheon for up to 10 guests Eight complimentary tickets to all CFAR events Hero Partner $7,500 per year Benefits All Key Partner benefits Logo on CFAR e-promotions for all ticketed events Dedicated banner ad on CFAR website Special plaque displayed at CFAR acknowledging sponsorship Six complimentary tickets to all CFAR events Key Partner $5,000 per year Benefits All Partner benefits Logo on Visitors Center video screen Monthly social media mentions Featured article in one CFAR newsletter Four complimentary tickets to all CFAR events Partner $2,500 per year Benefits Logo on CFAR website sponsor page Quarterly social media mentions Mention in CFAR newsletters Two complimentary tickets to all CFAR events Scholarship Sponsor Program In addition to the Annual Partners Program and Event Sponsorships, CFAR receives requests from schools, non-profits, special needs groups and others requesting tours to meet the Big Cats. While we attempt to help everyone, CFAR has ongoing expenses from veterinary care to feeding and enrichment expenses. As a Scholarship Sponsor, we will open a bank of tour passes in your company name and extend complimentary access to special groups. Scholarship Sponsorship Levels $2,500 Sponsorship 100 Sponsored Tour Tickets $5,000 Sponsorship 225 Sponsored Tour Tickets Scholarship Sponsors receive updates on the number of tickets distributed, the recipient groups’ name, and recognition in all social, print, and broadcast coverage. Scholarship Sponsor Recognition Scholarship Sponsors will receive: Company name and logo on CFAR website Names of groups that receive scholarship visits shown on CFAR website Distribution of a “Thanks for Visiting CFAR” to attendees, with company name and logo prominently displayed Rewards Based on Sponsorship Level CFAR is a volunteer driven, community supported reserve. Every contribution strengthens the future of big cats. Visibility and Brand Awareness Your company logo will be prominently displayed across various platforms, enhancing brand recognition among CFAR supporters and visitors. Community Engagement Sponsorship positions your business as a community leader supporting wildlife conservation and education. Exclusive Access Enjoy complimentary event tickets, private tours, and unique experiences at CFAR. Tax Benefits Contributions to CFAR may be tax-deductible, either as a charitable donation or as an advertising and marketing expense. Become a CFAR Partner Partnership opportunities are structured to align with CFAR’s mission and long-term goals. Inquire",
